menu "LoRa Protocol Configuration"

    config LORA_SEND_RELIABLE
        bool "Enable reliable transmission with ACK"
        default n
        help
            Enable reliable transmission mode in presenter mode.
            When enabled, presenter waits for ACK from PC with retries.
            When disabled, presenter sends fire-and-forget for lower latency.
            PC mode always sends ACKs regardless of this setting.

endmenu
